<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>12</span><span>14</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;李昌仁：《缘对论第九》，《玄妙镜》卷上，《藏外道书》第二十六册，第392页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>13</span><span>15</span><span>16</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;李昌仁：《三摇论十六》，《玄妙镜》卷上，《藏外道书》第二十六册，第394页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
